    "purpose": "Owns the server session runtime, total SessionEvent routing entrypoint, local task-originated event channel, shared session preview context with SessionContext::snapshot for prompt rendering, and task creation. Session accepts the client and host channels by role through accept_channel with ChannelEndpoint, leaving listener address resolution to the channel helper; route_session_event routes task, step, execution, and plan events back to the owning Task by task id and then calls send_client_event once.",
